{"tid":1633911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小弟心灰意冷 對海傾訴之時諗到啲野","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:29:32.000Z","uid":219111,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"008a3410afba36fb3b33fb5fee84a6ab64dc2c1c","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:44:52.000Z","msg":"香港抗爭多時 大家一直都做左好多文宣工作<br />\n亦有大型既和理非活動表達訴求<br />\n例如：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆 人鏈 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢啲方式往往都可以吸引到好多人既關注 包括媒體 以及外國人既眼睛<br />\n<br />\n但係，當一啲活動做得多，好快就會無左新鮮感，關注度亦會低左好多，所以我地既活動一定要創新，壯觀。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">重點黎啦</span></strong><br />\n小弟諗左個新既文宣方法，呢個方法亦好意象到我地活動其中一個核心理念Be water<br />\n<br />\n大家可以搵一日 一齊整張大型既banner 然後搵一堆可以浮係水上面既物料 造成一塊大型既浮板 再將banner貼係呢塊大型浮板上面 將佢推出大海 或者由泳手們hold住banner游出去 做完仲可以順手清下沙灘 等啲話我地淨係識破壞既人睇下 乜野叫做建設<br />\n<br />\n優點：<br />\n1. 未試過<br />\n2.夠大既話畫面都會幾壯觀<br />\n3.和理非，安全<br />\n4.低成本<br />\n5.高視角效果<br />\n6.我地平地做過，山又上過，唔試下水？<br />\n<br />\n缺點：<br />\n1. 回收問題（可用多條繩綁住，拉返黎回收）<br />\n2.可能影響海洋生物（我諗唔放得太出，淨係係沙灘綁繩放出去，應該海洋生物唔會受太大影響）<br />\n3. 需要大量可浮物資，或會做成垃圾/浪費（希望大家會自行收拾返啲野）<br />\n<br />\n我知道呢個時期做呢啲野可能無乜用，我自己都係勇武既一份子，可能成件事係有啲膠，但一式一味既文宣狀況已經愈黎愈乏味，影響關注度，加上呢個活動可以比超級大量既和理非手足參與，一家大細又可以參與。<br />\n<br />\n方案可行之處由大家商討，大家諗到啲咩優缺點，改良方案不妨提出討論，集思廣益。<br />\n<br />\n示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b6e9Pwc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb6e9Pwc.png&h=7268243d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n香港人 反抗</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"80a8b0d4535c7abdcbbf73823f498babe2c586ac","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"1推"},{"pid":"73fccf8f94e935fee7c89accfb5e22b783bdf439","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:35.000Z","msg":"2推"},{"pid":"21f45e2e7f45a78c8fa67a2deea5fef8303c333b","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"3推"},{"pid":"a31e9f501f4bb112f985c2d235cc63263f20031a","tid":1633911,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51556333c0c3e10cf0a8b887ad368e886dc24bb2","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:57.000Z","msg":"4推"},{"pid":"a4964120846cba21a2a0869dc5a80f8853f61b67","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:08.000Z","msg":"5推"},{"pid":"fd7648dae5709f8cccb6704cf9f46f577702516e","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:21.000Z","msg":"6推"},{"pid":"08a06791f0f972d26cf276ca9219a0659e3bc98a","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"7推"},{"pid":"25563a3466d9777b05e8a8e2d168dce7fbdc2eec","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"8推"},{"pid":"13c4cd5de52d969ade380f646d457c2da423fa91","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"9推"},{"pid":"95908c8653561552c326ea9518a2ed4964999dd4","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"10推"},{"pid":"dab597a5e35076de929dd03d7180a1ef39e06a52","tid":1633911,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80a8b0d4535c7abdcbbf73823f498babe2c586ac","tid":1633911,"uid":219111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:45:25.000Z","msg":"1推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:47:39.000Z","msg":"已經有人做過"},{"pid":"6d15202e77b12401560702545d7794fc64f8f57d","tid":1633911